Name: AGENT 00111
About the game: Agent 00111 is a platform puzzle that should become part of a hacker organization, you are assigned to take a test task, hack a computer. Each level is a puzzle that must be solved to bypass the security system. Solve problems and download megabytes of useful information. Game features - Solve puzzles to get information - Pump the abilities of the main character - To open some doors, you need to pass a mini game.
